WEBVTT

00:00:11.946 --> 00:00:15.350
This a very deep subject. 

00:00:21.546 --> 00:00:25.386
So, the- when the enlightenment of

00:00:25.387 --> 00:00:28.626
the Kundalini takes place

00:00:28.627 --> 00:00:37.336
in the brain, then the truth is

00:00:37.337 --> 00:00:39.557
perceived through your brain.

00:00:40.216 --> 00:00:42.217
That's why it's called as “satya khanda” [truth; bulb], 

00:00:42.217 --> 00:00:49.229
Means you start seeing the truth perceived by your brain.

00:00:49.896 --> 00:00:54.581
because so far whatever you see through your brain, 

00:00:54.581 --> 00:00:57.030
is not the truth.

00:00:57.738 --> 00:01:01.258
What you see, is just the outer side,

00:01:01.755 --> 00:01:04.001
say, you can see the colours.

00:01:04.788 --> 00:01:08.802
You can see the different aesthetics of the colours.

00:01:09.253 --> 00:01:12.753
You can see the quality of the thing.

00:01:13.319 --> 00:01:22.351
But you cannot say whether this carpet has been used by some saint. 

00:01:24.317 --> 00:01:29.683
You cannot say whether this is made by a devil or a divine person.

00:01:32.186 --> 00:01:40.014
You cannot say that this gentleman, is he a good person or he is an evil person. 

00:01:42.266 --> 00:01:48.946
You cannot say if this Deity has come out of the Mother Earth or not.

00:01:51.336 --> 00:02:02.614
Also, you cannot say about any person, who is your relation, 

00:02:03.299 --> 00:02:13.007
whether he is a good relation or a bad relation, 

00:02:13.007 --> 00:02:15.194
what sort of a person he is.or what sort of a person he is, 

00:02:15.389 --> 00:02:19.206
whether he goes to wrong people or to the right people, 

00:02:19.503 --> 00:02:24.405
whether he has connections with wrong side or with good side. 

00:02:25.338 --> 00:02:27.276
Here good means Divine.

00:02:28.671 --> 00:02:31.919
Now, the Spirit is expressed in the heart, 

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:33.968
is reflected in the heart.

00:02:34.400 --> 00:02:36.440
 the centre of the Spirit, 

00:02:36.440 --> 00:02:37.887
we can say, is in the heart. 

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:43.135
But actually, the seat of Spirit is above, here.

00:02:44.111 --> 00:02:48.638
And that is the Spirit what we call of the God Almighty, 

00:02:48.638 --> 00:02:56.724
Who say, Whom you call Parvardigar [Persian word], 

00:02:57.937 --> 00:03:02.332
you call Him Sadashiva or 

00:03:02.970 --> 00:03:07.530
 you can call Him, the Rahim 

00:03:09.322 --> 00:03:21.408
and you can call Him by many names which are said about the Lord who is God Almighty. 

00:03:22.830 --> 00:03:26.683
Niranjan, they call It, Nirahankar, 

00:03:26.852 --> 00:03:30.428
every sort of words which start with Nira, Nihi.

00:03:32.391 --> 00:03:34.556
Now, at every centre

00:03:37.852 --> 00:03:42.523
in the body you’ll receive a different type of joy. 

00:03:45.292 --> 00:03:53.852
Every centre has a different type of joy and there are names for every types of joy you receive at every centre 

00:03:53.852 --> 00:03:55.487
when the Kundalini rises. 

00:03:56.460 --> 00:04:00.588
But when the Kundalini comes into the Sahasrara, 

00:04:00.940 --> 00:04:07.258
then the joy you receive is called as Nirananda, Nirananda. 

00:04:07.741 --> 00:04:12.895
Now, Ni means nothing else but Ananda. Nirananda.

00:04:16.766 --> 00:04:20.640
Also, is surprising, my name is Nira – also,

00:04:20.641 --> 00:04:22.913
 in my family I’m called as Nira. 

00:04:23.880 --> 00:04:27.200
And Nira also means Mary, Maria.

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:30.040
 Because it means marine.

00:04:30.041 --> 00:04:34.440
Nira is water. Nira means water in Sanskrit language.

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:37.814
 It is called as Nirananda in the brain. 

00:04:39.112 --> 00:04:43.175
 And this stage ultimately unfolds.

00:04:43.912 --> 00:04:46.431
First what you know is the satya, 

00:04:47.193 --> 00:04:52.950
 is the truth – what is this another gentleman is suffering from,

00:04:54.546 --> 00:04:58.546
 that you see on your fingers. First you see your fingers.

00:04:59.067 --> 00:05:05.240
With your attention you know what chakras, what fingers are catching, with your attention.

00:05:06.210 --> 00:05:12.472
Then with your brain you can depict what centre, it is catching. 

00:05:12.691 --> 00:05:17.404
Because, if you say this finger, that doesn’t mean it is Vishuddhi Chakra.

00:05:17.807 --> 00:05:20.149
But your brain then says, “It is Vishuddhi.”

00:05:22.148 --> 00:05:28.402
And that depicts it that this fellow is suffering from the troubles of the Vishuddhi Chakra. 

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.890
But still it is rational. 

00:05:33.290 --> 00:05:37.615
Because you see what finger it catches and then you say it. 

00:05:37.615 --> 00:05:45.286
But when the “satya khanda” or the Sahasrara unfolds itself more,

00:05:46.117 --> 00:05:49.971
you don’t have to think about it, you just say it.

00:05:53.437 --> 00:05:58.759
Then there is no difference between your chitta and your satya.

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:08.249
The enlightened chitta and the enlightened brain become one.

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:16.263
There is no problem at all for such a person, there’s no need to see on the fingers, 

00:06:16.263 --> 00:06:21.065
 no need to say anything on the fingers and then depict it through brain.

00:06:21.744 --> 00:06:27.101
 Which you have learnt in Sahaja Yoga, that if you find something wrong here, 

00:06:27.101 --> 00:06:30.897
it means Agnya – that’s not necessary! You just say Agnya. And you just say it and it is there.

00:06:33.980 --> 00:06:36.000
Then it unfolds more.

00:06:39.978 --> 00:06:43.563
First it is integrated with, as I said, chitta.

00:06:45.077 --> 00:06:50.063
Then, when it gets absolutely integrated with the Spirit,

00:06:53.853 --> 00:07:00.000
then whatever you say, is the truth.

00:07:02.482 --> 00:07:04.454
You just say it, it is so. 

00:07:09.377 --> 00:07:17.536
That is how this brain unfolds into three new dimensions.

00:07:18.417 --> 00:07:26.671
First, it depicts the truth through logical conclusions. 

00:07:26.671 --> 00:07:33.677
Because, I have told you that if this finger is catching then it is Vishuddhi.

00:07:34.567 --> 00:07:37.541
And then you ask the person,And then you ask the person, “Have you got a problem here?”

00:07:37.541 --> 00:07:44.344
 He says, “Yes”. Then you believe in Me and then you believe that this is the Vishuddhi Chakra, 

00:07:44.344 --> 00:07:45.676
which is showing, is true.

00:07:46.580 --> 00:07:51.140
This is the logical conclusion, in a way, that you have experimented, 

00:07:52.340 --> 00:07:56.839
you are seeing and still doubting whether Mother says it’s true or not. 

00:07:57.138 --> 00:08:01.770
And then, you are sure, “Yes, it is so, we have seen that this is Vishuddhi Chakra.” 

00:08:01.770 --> 00:08:05.725
So, the truth becomes logically acceptable to his brain.

00:08:06.141 --> 00:08:10.112
But still, there is the brain working out on its gross level.

00:08:11.140 --> 00:08:14.084
Then the second stage, as I told you, 

00:08:17.780 --> 00:08:22.101
where you believe, you know for definite that this means Vishuddhi Chakra,

00:08:22.101 --> 00:08:26.763
no doubt about it. Nobody. Then – then we start “nirvikalpa” has started, 

00:08:26.763 --> 00:08:29.699
when there’s no doubt about Me or Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:30.362 --> 00:08:33.540
But then, the new unfolding starts within. 

00:08:35.210 --> 00:08:39.164
For that, one has to do meditation.

00:08:40.250 --> 00:08:43.930
In humility, one has to do meditation.

00:08:46.328 --> 00:08:57.111
And then also, for this new dimension,  where your chitta itself becomes merged into your brain 

00:08:57.820 --> 00:09:08.037
or into the enlightened brain, for that one has to very honestly and humbly surrender to Sahaja Yoga.

00:09:15.883 --> 00:09:22.189
So when you get it into your Sahasrara – yes, it is true Sahasrara was opened out [and]

00:09:22.384 --> 00:09:26.542
because of that you got this mass realisation.That’s true. 

00:09:26.864 --> 00:09:29.103
But now the quality has to go up.

00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:34.387
Quantity is quite big. The quality has to grow of the Sahasrara.

00:09:34.703 --> 00:09:47.288
And the Sahasrara is the
only instrument which is going to work out Sahaja Yoga in the modern times

00:09:48.395 --> 00:09:56.198
if we realise
that heart plays the most important role in Sahasrar.

00:09:57.070 --> 00:09:59.470
Just here (at the centre of Sahasrar)
is the heart centre.

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:07.964
How important it is that you have to recognise through your heart
otherwise this [Sahasrar] centre won’t open.

00:10:07.964 --> 00:10:09.946
Then how do you get your realisation? 

00:10:10.910 --> 00:10:13.072
What a beautiful connection made:

00:10:13.072 --> 00:10:18.554
that this centre here is the seat of the heart, is the peetha of
the heart. 

00:10:18.554 --> 00:10:20.633
And this has to open out.

00:10:20.634 --> 00:10:22.553
Then only does Kundalini comes in.

00:10:22.983 --> 00:10:30.997
So all this machinery is connected and made in such a manner that you have to understand 

00:10:30.997 --> 00:10:43.290
the importance of heart connected through this brain which is absolutely integrated with heart.

00:10:44.783 --> 00:10:48.544
Sahasrara is the one to be preserved.

00:10:49.609 --> 00:10:57.499
[Not just] by putting left to the right, right to the left and everything, opening it out but by recognition.

00:10:58.463 --> 00:11:02.465
With introspection
also, you can ask, “Why can’t I recognise that way?

00:11:02.465 --> 00:11:05.987
Why can’t I do that way? What is my
interest?”

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:12.000
Now, if you come to Sahaja Yoga for making some sort of a power game,

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:18.705
you want to have a power, you are finished.You want to have money or some sort of a business, you are finished.

00:11:18.705 --> 00:11:25.901
Anything else you try like making something for your children or for your marriage or family or

00:11:25.901 --> 00:11:32.053
any such outward things if you come to Sahaja Yoga this won’t work out.

00:11:32.443 --> 00:11:37.309
But just to expand your heart, to spread your love to everyone,

00:11:37.309 --> 00:11:47.003
to feel their love within your
heart and then to put yourself into a position when it responds,

00:11:47.003 --> 00:12:00.008
the heart responds, to divinity within you and to your Mother with full mental activity of the heart.

00:12:02.133 --> 00:12:08.384
Today’s subject may sound rather difficult for you to understand but I had to say this one day

00:12:08.708 --> 00:12:14.053
because we are quite satisfied with a little of the Kundalini coming out of our head.

00:12:14.454 --> 00:12:16.133
There’s so much to come out.

00:12:16.134 --> 00:12:23.552
So much divinity is there which has to come out and if you
have to ascend and if you are the foundation of that new age

00:12:23.552 --> 00:12:28.067
which is going to transform
the whole world we’ll have to work hard.

00:12:29.163 --> 00:12:33.484
We shouldn’t say, “I don’t know how to get up in
the morning. I don’t know.”

00:12:33.484 --> 00:12:37.143
You are on a warpath. You are soldiers now.

00:12:37.644 --> 00:12:45.430
And you have to work it out if you have to fight the forces of ignorance and darkness.

00:12:47.483 --> 00:12:48.852
This has to be worked out.

00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:52.587
This has to be paid attention to.

00:12:53.731 --> 00:13:02.941
So what you have to do is absolutely decide within yourself today that, “We are going to work it out in such a way

00:13:02.941 --> 00:13:11.376
that we will all become very powerful Sahaja Yogis and through
us the whole world is going to be saved.”

00:13:24.173 --> 00:13:33.205
Now, what experience you should have to build that in your heart is the point.

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:49.946
And the
experience is of your own divinity, of your own spirituality.

00:13:54.000 --> 00:14:00.191
spirituality. Once you start developing that
experience

00:14:01.777 --> 00:14:04.769
then you know that you are a divine person.

00:14:06.639 --> 00:14:12.000
Unless and until you are aware
fully that you are a divine person

00:14:15.071 --> 00:14:22.080
howsoever faith you may have in Me the recognition is
not complete.

00:14:22.080 --> 00:14:24.848
Because who is recognising Me? Is a blind person.

00:14:26.210 --> 00:14:33.006
If a blind person is
recognising Me it won’t have that response of the heart.

00:14:34.861 --> 00:14:41.812
So, first you have to recognise yourself to be a divine person, to have faith in yourself.

00:14:44.589 --> 00:14:48.610
We
do not have faith in ourselves, though we are Sahaja Yogis.

00:14:49.069 --> 00:14:51.713
If there’s any problem, they
will write a letter to Me.

00:14:53.879 --> 00:14:56.158
If they are sick they’ll write a letter to Me.

00:14:58.519 --> 00:15:01.797
If there’s any family
questioning they’ll write to Me.

00:15:03.957 --> 00:15:07.916
If there’s somebody bothering them with some questions
they’ll ask Me.

00:15:11.719 --> 00:15:13.959
But if you become introspective

00:15:15.466 --> 00:15:20.853
and meditative then you touch that divinity
within you.

00:15:21.876 --> 00:15:26.794
When you touch that divinity you know you are a divine person.

00:15:27.809 --> 00:15:34.947
So, in Sahasrara Puja, actually, you have to recognise your own divinity, that you are
divine,

00:15:35.569 --> 00:15:38.049
by experiencing your divinity.

00:15:39.089 --> 00:15:41.558
How do you experience your divinity?

00:15:44.878 --> 00:15:50.460
That you give realisation to others. 

00:15:51.390 --> 00:15:56.200
It’s a great experience to give realisation to others.

00:15:57.019 --> 00:16:02.919
Not only that, you
give realisation but you can tell about their chakras,

00:16:03.659 --> 00:16:07.708
you know what’s wrong with them –
you are quite confident.

00:16:10.077 --> 00:16:19.805
And mentally you know that, “Yes, yes, it’s working” you’ll say,
without getting involved into it as “I do it!”

00:16:19.805 --> 00:16:23.729
You’ll say, “Mother, it’s working. It’s happening.
It’s this thing, that thing.”

00:16:26.170 --> 00:16:29.532
But you never introspect, 

00:16:30.469 --> 00:16:31.989
“How is it I am working?

00:16:36.406 --> 00:16:37.859
How I’m working it out?

00:16:40.739 --> 00:16:42.000
How I can feel it? 

00:16:44.040 --> 00:16:45.642
What has happened to me?

00:16:48.739 --> 00:16:50.979
What has improved in me?

00:16:52.019 --> 00:16:53.859
 What has sharpened in me?

00:16:55.059 --> 00:16:58.659
What is the development in me? 

00:16:59.619 --> 00:17:01.198
What is the transformation?”

00:17:06.571 --> 00:17:13.748
Once you start thinking about it, the experience of your own being,

00:17:14.039 --> 00:17:24.000
then a kind of a feeling
– feeling – towards the Mahamaya, develops.

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.499
Feeling. Again, I say ‘feeling’.

00:17:26.821 --> 00:17:33.110
Like feeling of fear, feeling of happiness, feeling of depression.

00:17:33.110 --> 00:17:35.682
Any feeling you develop. 

00:17:37.909 --> 00:17:45.641
And this feeling, you could call a feeling of gratitude, feeling of love,

00:17:46.508 --> 00:17:51.261
feeling of oneness, feeling of joy.

00:17:52.957 --> 00:18:07.824
All
this starts working in your heart and then you feel the responses.

00:18:11.279 --> 00:18:21.057
If, supposing, the sea is
responding to moon that means it has that mobility in it to respond.

00:18:21.057 --> 00:18:24.000
 A stone will not react to the moon.

00:18:25.052 --> 00:18:27.187
In the same way: in your heart 

00:18:27.569 --> 00:18:34.809
these waves of these feelings are created by the
experience of spirituality,

00:18:35.050 --> 00:18:40.249
by the experience of your own being. 

00:18:41.449 --> 00:18:44.748
And then you start expressing them.

00:18:46.440 --> 00:18:49.506
And I could make it out.

00:18:50.419 --> 00:18:56.260
Such a person may not be so much talkative,
may not know much about Sahaja Yoga,

00:18:56.260 --> 00:18:57.619
but in the heart,

00:18:59.779 --> 00:19:02.812
in the heart he feels a response.

00:19:05.523 --> 00:19:15.977
Is something to be achieved because you know that the centre of heart is placed here.

00:19:17.229 --> 00:19:20.939
The peetha, the seat, of the Heart, is on Brahmarandhra.

00:19:22.909 --> 00:19:26.838
If your heart is not open,

00:19:26.838 --> 00:19:31.804
in the heart if you do not have those responses built-in…

00:19:36.398 --> 00:19:38.677
they need not be of awe or fear.

00:19:40.599 --> 00:19:44.155
But a natural protocol that develops. 

00:19:46.135 --> 00:19:53.456
Then you can never do
wrong because you know what ever is good in your heart.

00:19:55.193 --> 00:20:00.000
 Supposing you love somebody
from your heart – you are not going to harm that person.

00:20:02.036 --> 00:20:08.459
In the same way, when you start
feeling those responses in your heart, 

00:20:08.459 --> 00:20:13.954
you can never do wrong because they are now
manifesting which were built within you.

00:20:14.370 --> 00:20:16.609
Because there was spirituality, 

00:20:16.610 --> 00:20:20.905
there was that
divinity which was built in. Now it is manifesting.

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:14.570
We all have to be very peaceful people and you have seen, My peaceful nature has solved so many problems just like that.

00:21:14.840 --> 00:21:17.583
So try to achieve that peace within you.

00:21:17.583 --> 00:21:20.303
That peace should not be lost at any cost,

00:21:20.303 --> 00:21:28.220
and should not be also expressed outside in a way, like I sometimes. My peace itself becomes terrible. 

00:21:29.080 --> 00:21:32.977
But you don’t have that kind of a
possibility, so you just don’t do it.

00:21:33.001 --> 00:21:35.777
You just don’t do it, never do it that way.

00:21:35.801 --> 00:21:41.072
Try to be extremely peaceful, try to make your forehead relaxed.

00:21:41.492 --> 00:21:44.469
Many people come to Me with [face] like this,you see (distorted, twisted face),

00:21:44.469 --> 00:21:47.621
then I just know that there is a big bhoot on the head
sitting,

00:21:47.621 --> 00:21:48.820
then I shout at them.

00:21:49.698 --> 00:21:53.642
Keep your forehead relaxed, relaxed. “I am not doing anything,

00:21:53.642 --> 00:21:56.661
Mother
is doing everything. Relax, relax, relax.”

00:21:56.661 --> 00:22:01.146
If you relax you’ll find that your
heart will open.

00:22:02.420 --> 00:22:04.100
“My heart cannot open.”

00:22:04.101 --> 00:22:06.100
Why, why can’t you open your heart?

00:22:06.101 --> 00:22:10.954
Because you have no trust
in yourself. Try to trust yourself.

00:22:11.147 --> 00:22:16.201
Open your Agnya, open your Ekadasha and your Sahasrara,

00:22:16.201 --> 00:22:17.640
and your heart will open.

00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:22.589
Once your Sahasrara is open, your heart will open automatically, 

00:22:31.753 --> 00:22:36.395
At the level of Sahasrara, you know the Truth.

00:22:38.231 --> 00:22:45.762
So all kinds of illusions, all kinds of
misunderstandings,

00:22:46.575 --> 00:22:52.082
all kinds of self-imposed ignorance,

00:22:52.703 --> 00:22:54.703
they all have to disappear,

00:22:56.303 --> 00:23:01.268
because what you know is the Truth.

00:23:01.580 --> 00:23:08.329
The Truth is not sharp, it’s not harsh,

00:23:08.940 --> 00:23:14.196
it is not something which is difficult to assimilate.

00:23:16.153 --> 00:23:27.413
People thought Truth must be something that
would be just very damaging or could be very harsh,

00:23:27.874 --> 00:23:31.565
could create problems between human beings.

00:23:32.413 --> 00:23:35.288
It should not have, it should not have,

00:23:36.194 --> 00:23:37.794
it was not meant to be,

00:23:38.493 --> 00:23:40.580
but whenever they talked of Truth,

00:23:41.100 --> 00:23:45.097
the people used it for a wrong purpose.

00:23:46.173 --> 00:23:54.964
It’s something special about
human beings that they start using things for a wrong attitude,

00:23:54.964 --> 00:24:02.863
for a wrong message and try to use it for their own purpose.

00:24:05.023 --> 00:24:11.612
It’s such a common thing with human beings that they
want to have power over other men.

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:15.643
Only your Sahasrara can reflect the light of the Divine.

00:24:16.059 --> 00:24:18.693
So, your Sahasrara is extremely
important.

00:24:19.590 --> 00:24:24.492
You must meditate to enrich your Sahasrara, to cure it,

00:24:24.492 --> 00:24:27.649
to make it completely nourished by the Kundalini.

00:24:28.471 --> 00:24:35.636
There’s no need to do many rituals, but meditation and also
little bit of taking bandhan,

00:24:35.636 --> 00:24:38.229
even now, today, is necessary, I think,

00:24:39.539 --> 00:24:41.226
when you go out,

00:24:42.000 --> 00:24:50.628
because still Kali Yuga is working its own pangs and Satya Yuga is trying to come out.

00:24:51.840 --> 00:24:54.199
We are the ones who are going to support,

00:24:54.880 --> 00:25:02.242
look after the Satya Yuga and that’s why the
Sahasrara opening is very, very important.

00:25:02.960 --> 00:25:04.082
It’s very important

00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:12.648
and those who want to grow
should meditate every day,

00:25:12.648 --> 00:25:14.860
whatever time you may come home,

00:25:14.861 --> 00:25:18.208
maybe in the morning,
maybe in the evening, any time.

00:25:18.208 --> 00:25:23.806
But you will know that you are meditating when you can get into thoughtless awareness,

00:25:24.254 --> 00:25:27.108
then you will know. Your reaction will be zero.

00:25:27.421 --> 00:25:29.280
Look at something, you will just look at it.

00:25:29.661 --> 00:25:32.163
You won’t react, because you are thoughtless.

00:25:33.580 --> 00:25:36.829
You won’t react. When that reaction is not
there,

00:25:37.407 --> 00:25:41.572
then everything, you will be surprised, is Divine,

00:25:42.496 --> 00:25:46.230
because reaction is your Agnya’s
problem.

00:25:46.917 --> 00:25:50.359
Once you are absolutely thoughtlessly aware,

00:25:50.359 --> 00:25:52.118
you are one with the Divine.

00:25:52.597 --> 00:25:56.968
So much so that Divine takes over every activity,

00:25:57.477 --> 00:26:04.915
every moment of your life and looks after you and you feel completely secured,

00:26:05.303 --> 00:26:09.519
one with the Divine and enjoy the blessings of the Divine.

00:26:10.001 --> 00:26:11.121
May God bless you.
